videos.description: Matisse Thybulle picks off the pass then dribbles up the court for an uncontested dunk.
videos.headline: Washington's Thybulle steals and rocks the rim

videos.description: Noah Dickerson gathers the loose ball and finishes with an emphatic dunk.
videos.headline: Washington's Dickerson throws down with authority

videos.description: David Crisp outhustles Boise State players to the loose ball then Noah Dickerson uses a nice post move for a layup.
videos.headline: Washington's Crisp lays out for loose ball

videos.description: Matisse Thybulle spots up and drains the 3-pointer with a defender in his face.
videos.headline: Washington's Thybulle gets a 4-point play
